Release Notes:

Robotic Empire is thrilled to announce the label's second tribute to Nirvana;
this time, the seminal "Nevermind" album is given the cover treatment by a
diverse range of bands.

With artwork inspired by and mutated from the original album, Whatever Nevermind
features contributions from Boris, Cave In, Circa Survive, Kylesa, La Dispute,
Nothing, Pygmy Lush, Thou, Torche, Touche Amore, White Reaper, Wrong and Young
Widows
